assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Sanyo Electric Railway Co.,Ltd. engages in transportation and real estate businesses in Japan. The company also operates ropeways and amusement park; and rents and sells real estate properties. In addition, it is involved in passenger car transportation, travel, taxi, automobile management contract, food service, and land and building business. Further, the company engages in the ticket consignment sales, futsal court rental, department and merchandise store, advertising, and insurance agency activities, as well as paid employment agency, security, and business processing contract businesses. Additionally, the company engages in the vehicle construction, civil engineering surveying, design and construction, automobile maintenance, electrical construction, and train cleaning businesses. Furthermore, the company is involved in the development of computer software and information processing services, as well as building maintenance, mat mop rental, and pest control businesses. Sanyo Electric Railway Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1907 and is headquartered in Akashi, Japan.
